Class AutoWaitInjector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qmetry.qaf.automation.ui.selenium.AutoWaitInjector

    SeleniumCommandListener

    public class AutoWaitInjector
extends java.lang.Object
implements SeleniumCommandListener
    com.qmetry.qaf.automation.ui.selenium.AutoWaitInjector.java
    SeleniumCommandListener implementation for automatic wait injection before executing command. To provide exclude command list set property auto.wait.exclude.commands. <
    By default this listener is get registered. If you want to skip this listener, provide property ApplicationProperties.SKIP_AUTO_WAIT (selenium.skip.autowait) value to false. list of commands that will: click, mouse, select, type, getText, check,getElement,removeSelection,addSelection,focus To provide exclude commands set property ApplicationProperties.AUTO_WAIT_EXCLUDE_CMD To provide include commands set property auto.wait.include.commands

    chirag
